description: Ukraine's president is still popular after a year in power but his top team has fallen apart.
title: Zelensky's Ukraine: Why comic's dream of transformation may be over
title_page: Zelensky's Ukraine: Why comic's dream of transformation may be over - BBC News
maintext: President Zelensky has packed a lot into the first year and there are four to go. Plenty of people, particularly in Kyiv, will tell you that it's heading towards inevitable disaster; that history will repeat itself and it will all end with street demonstrations.
